yingyinNormal.en: Analysis. Why did you ask me about my son?
yingyinNormal.zh: 分析模式，你为什么问起我儿子？

yingyinNormal.en: So, what do you do? Mostly player analysis right now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你都干些什么？目前主要做球员分析。

yingyinNormal.en: Got it. Seen it. Detailed analysis posted online.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有了。看过了。我的详细分析已经发到网上了。

yingyinNormal.en: Voice analysis points to western Tennessee, Memphis area.
yingyinNormal.zh: 语音分析将歹徒身份指向田纳西西部孟菲斯地区。

yingyinNormal.en: Maeve, analysis. Who made these changes to your code? Jesus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 梅芙，分析模式，是谁篡改了你的代码？天啊。

yingyinNormal.en: More data, more analysis, less likelihood of a terrorist attack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数据越多，分析越全面，发生恐怖袭击的可能性就越低。

yingyinNormal.en: Not bad. Thank you for that analysis. Now, let's just focus on you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不错嘛。感谢你的分析，现在，聊聊你吧。

yingyinNormal.en: While we develop a system to help you determine how much intelligence to act on which attacks to stop, which to let through. Statistical analysis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在形成的系统下就能帮你分析情报，部署进攻停止或是放弃。数据分析。

yingyinNormal.en: That's because it's protected by gait analysis. A step beyond facial recognition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为它使用的是步态分析，比面部识别更加先进。

yingyinNormal.en: But MRI analysis has shown that MDMA actually increases communication in these regions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但核磁共振成像分析，摇头丸确实可以增强这两块区域的链接。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if you look at it like that, I mean that's proper scientific analysis. You can't argue with science.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果从你这个角度来分析的话，的确有科学理论根据，你争不过科学的。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry about him. Alright. All he has to do is install the fake profile before I get to the gait analysis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心他，好吗？他只要在我进入步态分析之前，把伪造的档案导入就行了。

yingyinNormal.en: Analysis. What motivated your attack on Clementine? A cognitive error triggered my Good Samaritan reflex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 分析模式，你攻击克莱门汀的动机是什么？一个认知错误触发了我的仁慈撒玛利亚人反射。

yingyinNormal.en: You've allowed no time for analysis or decision-making. In these simulations, you've taken all of the humanity out of the cockpit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里面没有分析和决策过程，所有的计算机模拟，你们都把人类因素排除在驾驶舱外。

yingyinNormal.en: Threat analysis? Massoud Shammar, Tariq al Juhani, Osman Ahmed, Yasin Said. Radicalized Muslims, masters level software engineers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 威胁分析？马苏德·沙马尔，塔里克·尤哈尼奥斯曼·艾哈迈德，亚辛·赛义德，激进穆斯林大师级软件工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: I had a great idea. You know how we're always having to stop and solve differential equations, like when you're doing Fourier analysis, or using the Schr dinger equation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有个好主意，我们总会被迫停下工作去解某些微分方程式吧，比如你做傅里叶分析的时候或是用到薛定谔方程的时候？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, Evelyn did a cost-benefit analysis comparing all your last five years of crime fighting before going underground. And Elastigirl's numbers are self-explanatory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 伊芙琳做了一个收益和损耗的分析对比了你们在转入地下前的五年里所有打击犯罪的行动。弹力女超人的出色成绩不言而喻。

yingyinNormal.en: 18 years ago, I sent the FBI crime lab samples from a bag of excrement that had been lit on fire on my front porch for fingerprinting and DNA analysis. Why haven't I heard back yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 十八年前有人在我的门廊上点燃了一包粪便，我从中提取了样本寄给了联调局的罪案鉴证科，为了提取指纹和化验DNA，为什么我到现在还没收到任何回复呢？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The great question is who should benefit from the <highlight>analysis</highlight> of all the data that our lives now generate.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最大的问题是，谁应该从我们生活中产生的所有数据分析中受益。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Analyses</highlight> reveal that the number of papers including the keywords "environmental change" or "climate change" have increased rapidly since 2004.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 分析显示，自2004年以来，包括关键词“环境变化”或“气候变化”在内的论文数量迅速增加。

examination_example.sentence: Neither of these patterns is borne out by the <highlight>analysis</highlight>, suggesting that the structures of the languages are lineage-specific and not governed by universals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这两种模式都没有得到分析的证实，这表明语言的结构是谱系特异性的，不受普遍性的支配。
